{"tid":923604,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"就黎移民 唔捨得香港既一切","createTime":"2018-12-01T11:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T02:08:16.000Z","uid":136933,"like":8,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"1884b327435988333260ba030319f14d83e6ac1a","tid":923604,"uid":136933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"去到一個朋友都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒撚去到都唔知識唔識到朋友<br />\n唔敢同人一齊<br />\n因為知道自己就黎走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我真係好中意香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想繼續係香港讀埋最後兩年書<br />\n好想同班朋友影畢業相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到呢一刻 我都係唔敢相信呢個事實<br />\n我係咪就要走喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好冇真實感"},{"pid":"e868beaed24fd6972a73413ca493519f6f12c08e","tid":923604,"uid":115535,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"好好珍惜"},{"pid":"502000afe9c247316000805bb45d1efed9cc26f4","tid":923604,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:52:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>狗</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92acc9e4a1c1fc862b1a6ec9bc151c83158e0ae1","tid":923604,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:53:47.000Z","msg":"去邊定居"},{"pid":"ad8ec8582cb4941e5925bb20ab01affc08269914","tid":923604,"uid":136933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e868beaed24fd6972a73413ca493519f6f12c08e","tid":923604,"uid":115535,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"好好珍惜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:54:38.000Z","msg":"可以點珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲未同我班朋友開口"